ReadMe News Articles Summarizer Ninaad Pai
Project developed in Python 2.7.9
This a news article summarizer developed in Python using NLTK, Date:29th April 2015
The program recognizes xml type news data and creates summary of 4-5 lines using minimum and maximum cut of word frequency
The news articles are extracted from BBC live news feed
To see web page go to http://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/rss.xml
The program asks for URL and number of articles to be summarized
 Steps for running project:

1.To run project extract .zip file 
2. Go to extracted location in command prompt
3. Execute command python summarizer.py
4. After successful execution the program will ask for news feed URL
5. Provide above URL for Top Stories news articles on BBC 
6. Provide number of articles to be summarized
7. For different types of news articles see information below

